The could be due to a permissions issue. Let us know if this works. 

[Grant League permission to run on your computer!](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions)

http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/Annie_3.jpg

This is a great starting point. Because League interacts with files and programs outside of the League folder, it's important for it to run with proper system permissions. 

If you still encounter issues after following the permissions guide, let me know.
